# KGHub Production Server

## Connection

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| IP | `160.153.185.4` |
| SSH Port | `2222` |
| Deploy user | `kghubdeploy` (password in team vault) |
| App user | `kghubapp` (owns `/opt/kghub/app`, runs PM2) |
| cPanel user | `kghubweb` (owns `kghub.ai` vhosts) |
